<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>Zumi</author>
<hymn_number>220</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Ka maah luigal khuo hawih chu a um,
 Tun ka ngaklah khawpi hawih chu;
 Lungdeih cheng cheng a kimnau mun,
 Muh nuomin ka thil chim thei puoi.

[V2]
 Aw chieh lai I hiu, kichawl puoi tiu;
 Lalpa hatna suongin, khawpi hawih zuon hitiu.

[V3]
 2. Zie khawpi hawih lam chu zuon zel hitiu,
 Chawllo in chieh zel hitiu ie;
 Galmuonna mun him a um puoi,
 Lalpa kawm I tun ma cheng un.

[V4]
 3. Hechien maizen leng chu pak chim puong ka,
 Gal lauhna ah leng mah leng le;
 Van mun lopi tun tieng chu leh,
 Pakna la daih ka gingcha puoi.

[V5]
 4. Aw, van Thagau Thiengtho hung leng inla,
 Lung gilo khaksa hawng kitin;
 Na gam hawihah ei pui inla,
 Kipah tawp ngei lohna achun.</lyrics>
<title>Aw Chieh Lai I Hiu</title>
</song>